                           <h2 style="color:#ffcc66">ACCOUNT SETTINGS</h2>
                           <h3>Q. Edit Proﬁle Picture?</h3>
                                You can edit your profile picture by going to Profile > Edit Profile > . You can upload your photo from your gallery. For editing other details, you can fill it manually in each sections in the same page.<br><br>
                            <h3>Q. How to Post a Feed?</h3>
                                It is made simple as you can either click on the top input box or from the left side in the feed or home page. You will be redirected to a special page that allows you to post a feed by writing your thoughts and uploading images.
                        </p>
