                            <h2 style="color:#ffcc66">QUERIES</h2>
                            <h3>Q. My scrolling is not smooth. Can you help?</h3>
                            This issue may occur with certain devices. Please reach out to <a href="mailto:redressal@buzztalk.com">redressal@buzztalk.com</a> for more information. We are also constantly working to improve user experience.
                            <h3>Q. Why is the app slow?</h3>
                            In our recent update we have released a faster and better UI. . Please check your internet speed, clear your cache files or restart the phone. If the problem still persists, kindly drop us an email at <a href="mailto:redressal@buzztalk.com">redressal@buzztalk.com</a> along with your handle and screen recording or screenshot.
                            <h3>Q. I see a lot of abusive/hateful language. What can I do?</h3>
                            Abusive and hateful language is something we do not encourage on BuzzTalk and require all content to comply with our <a href="./guidelines.html" >Community Guidelines</a>. Please use our in app reporting feature to report such BuzzTalk. A review will be made based on legal guidelines and community reporting. To report a BuzzTalk, please use the two dots on the top right corner of a BuzzTalk and from the index choose Report BuzzTalk. A BuzzTalk can be reported for any of the reasons listed in the index.
                            <h3>Q. Someone is impersonating me, what can I do?</h3>
                            If someone is impersonating you then please report such a profile. To report, please use the two dots on the top right corner of a BuzzTalk and from the index choose Report User. A User can be reported for any of the reasons listed in the index including “pretending to be me or someone else”.
                        </p>
