                            <h3>Q. Someone is posting nude and/or objectionable or content related to child abuse. How can I report it?</h3>
                            You can report using the "Report BuzzTalk" or "Report User" option within the BuzzTalk App. To report a BuzzTalk, please use the two dots on the top right corner of a BuzzTalk and from the index choose Report BuzzTalk. A BuzzTalk can be reported for any of the reasons listed in the index including Graphic, Obscene or Sexual Content.<br><br>
